## Reference Documents
# Always read the relevant doc before implementing anything.
# These are in the docs/ folder — use @docs/ to reference them in Cursor.

- PRD (features, scope, user flows, success metrics):
    docs/prd.md
- Design + Architecture (components, colors, fonts, spacing, state, data flow, API routes):
    docs/design-doc.md
- Tech Stack (setup commands, code patterns, folder structure, starter code):
    docs/tech-stack.md
